{
  "texts": [
    "Due to the iterative process of writing prompts on ChatGPT, we started with the least amount of information to gauge how much direction the LLM needed to produce useful results.",
    "Initially, we gave ChatGPT one Twitter bio and simply asked it to identify lifestyle words (see Prompt #1).",
    "After this first prompt attempt, we notice one thing.",
    "ChatGPT is unsure about what counts as lifestyles, something we had implicitly in mind when manually coding the selection of Twitter bios by hand, but did not specify for the LLM.",
    "Furthermore, there are some things in our codebook that have not been picked up by the LLM."
  ]
}